reviewText: Terrible movie.  This was a complete waste of time and money.  It was so bad, we shut it off before the movie was over.  There were maybe a couple scenes that were funny, but besides that, it was bad.  You could tell it was a low budget movie.  I wouldn't be surprised if the total budget on the movie was $1000.

reviewText: I repeat, I don't take movies seriously.  Pure entertainment.  This was it.  I laughed throughout this movie!  It was funny to me, and I read the reviews and I don't care.  It has a big cast and even though I can see why it went straight to DVD, it gave me laughing fits from beginning to end.  It was a hot ghetto mess and I totally took to it.  Russ Parr, you did it again and I commend you!
summary: Should come with a warning label:  PLEASE DON'T TAKE SERIOUSLY.
